::Hakibuscon::

           Hakibuscon was hit in the back by Oinker's shots, and went
forward but got hit by Punch's shots, sending him  up in the air, spiraling,
a little to the left.  He lay on the ground, in much pain.  He aimed his gun
up at Punch's head, but dropped his gun, and then his arm fell back to the
ground.

        "I hate to admit
it......but....but......I....I....I.....Surrender....Mercy....I beg of
you!!!  Mercy!!!  Please, I'll do anything....anything you want......I'll
even join you permanently!!!!" He said, trying to lift his hand.
